# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your real values.
#
# Google Maps JavaScript API key — required for the *web* build of the picker.
# Set up your key at https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials and
# enable both:
#   - Maps JavaScript API
#   - Places API (New)
# See README.md → "Web setup" for the full setup walkthrough.
#
# This env var is *only* read on the web platform. iOS and Android use the
# same Google Maps API key but read it from app.json instead — see
# `example/app.json` → expo.android.config.googleMaps.apiKey.
EXPO_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=YOUR_KEY
